Body:
with expected_protocol(ik.generic_scpi.SCPIMultimeter, ['CONF?', 'CONF?',
    'CONF?', 'CONF:FRES +1.000000E+01,MIN', 'CONF?',
    'CONF:CURR:DC +1.000000E+01,3e-06'], [
    'VOLT +1.000000E+01,+3.000000E-06', 'VOLT +1.000000E+01,MAX',
    'FRES +1.000000E+01,+3.000000E-06', 'CURR:DC +1.000000E+01,+3.000000E-06']
    ) as dmm:
    assert dmm.resolution == 3e-06
    assert dmm.resolution == dmm.Resolution.maximum
    dmm.resolution = dmm.Resolution.minimum
    dmm.resolution = 3e-06
